            <p class="section-label reveal"><i class="fa-regular fa-bell"></i> &nbsp;Stay in the loop</p>
            <h2 class="reveal">Want to be the first to know?</h2>
            <p class="reveal">Sign up to our newsletter to know when our apps launch on the stores, for updates,
              behind-the-scenes content, and early access opportunities!</p>
            <div class="newsletter-form reveal" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
              <a href="https://kidamame.substack.com/subscribe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn-white">
                ✨ Join our newsletter
              </a>
            </div>
            <p class="form-note reveal">No spam. Unsubscribe any time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

